{"title":"Palsamid","description":"","products":[{"product_id":"linden-flower-conditioner-with-nordic-birch-extract-250ml","title":"Magrada Hair Stimulating Conditioner with Linden Flower Extract 250ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https:\/\/www.magrada.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/1-2-300x300.png\" alt=\"anne stiil ilulemmik 2019\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https:\/\/www.magrada.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/2-2-300x300.png\" alt=\"iluteemant proff soovitab\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\"\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eEnjoy midsummer moments all year round. This conditioner is characterised by a composition of efficient Nordic plants which supports and accelerates natural hair growth. The silky, creamy composition of the conditioner spreads evenly on the hair, leaving behind a slightly honey-like aroma – like a warm July night.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe Nordic birch extract moisturises and softens the hair, making it easy to comb. The organic aloe extract has an calming effect on the scalp and prevents drying of the tips. The composition of plant extracts gives the hair a healthy shine, protects it from heat treatment, and preserves the pigmentation of the hair follicles, helping the hair to remain lively and elastic. The light conditioner is suitable for the entire family for daily use.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eNordic linden flower extract \u003c\/span\u003ehas a moisturising and softening effect suitable for a sensitive or irritated scalp.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eThe organic Nordic birch extract \u003c\/span\u003estimulates the circulation in the scalp and strengthens the roots, thereby accelerating natural hair growth.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eThe organic aloe extract \u003c\/span\u003ehas a deeply calming and moisturising effect on the skin. Aloe is well-known for its rich vitamin A, C, and E, folic acid, and collagen content.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply the conditioner on your hair after shampooing, starting from the tips. Leave in for 2–3 minutes, then rinse with plenty of water. The conditioner is suitable for daily use.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eStore at a temperature of 5 to 25 degrees. When storing, protect from direct sunlight. Do not store the product near heaters or other heat sources.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Cetearyl Alcohol, Cetrimonium Chloride, Glycerin, Behentrimonium Methosulfate, Parfum, Cetyl Alcohol, Betula Alba (Birch) Leaf Exract*, Aloe Barbadensis (Aloe Vera) Extract*, Butylene Glycol, Alcohol, Tilia Cordata (Linden Flower) Extract, Phenoxyethanol, Ethylhexylglycerin, Potassium Sorbate, Sodium Benzoate, Hexyl Cinnamal, Geraniol\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e*COSMOS Certified Organic Ingredient\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIngredients of natural origin: 92,77%.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe list of ingredients may be changed. Please see the packaging for the updated and most accurate list of ingredients.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eparaben-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e sulphate-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e silicone-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e vegan\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e | cruelty-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e hand-made \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e with a minimal list of ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Magrada Organic Cosmetics","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":48927685542215,"sku":"","price":12.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/magrada-hair-stimulating-conditioner-with-linden-flower-extract-250ml-1045756.png?v=1763665703"},{"product_id":"volumizing-solid-conditioner-with-linden-flower-extract","title":"Magrada Volumizing Solid Conditioner With Linden Flower Extract 50g","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eGentle on your hair and on the environment. The solid conditioner is eco-friendly and practical to take with you in your suitcase or workout bag.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe combination of the best natural ingredients restores and nourishes hair without making it heavy. Plant-based ingredients, such as linden flowers, cocoa butter, shea butter, and sweet almond oil, leave the hair soft and pliable with a hint of a sweet linden flower aroma reminding you of a warm midsummer night.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eNordic linden flower extract \u003c\/span\u003ehas a moisturising and softening effect suitable for a sensitive or irritated scalp.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eShea butter\u003c\/span\u003e is extracted from the nuts of the shea tree, which is native to Africa. Shea butter softens and moisturises the skin and helps to maintain its moisture balance.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eCocoa butter\u003c\/span\u003e contains plenty of essential fatty acids, which help to improve the protective function of the skin.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003ePro-vitamin B5 \u003c\/span\u003eadds healthy elasticity and shine to your tresses and improves the structure of processed hair.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eAfter washing your hair with a shampoo, massage the conditioner gently into wet ends and then rinse.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Cetearyl Alcohol, Theobroma Cacao (Cocoa) Seed Butter, Behentrimonium Methosulfate, Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter, Prunus Amygdalus Dulcis (Sweet Almond) Oil, Parfum, Tilia Cordata (Linden) Flower Extract, Hexyl Cinnamal, Geraniol\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIngredients of natural origin: 99%.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe list of ingredients may be changed. Please see the packaging for the updated and most accurate list of ingredients.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eparaben-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e SLS-free | alcohol-free\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e silicone-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e vegan\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e cruelty-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e hand-made \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e with a minimal list of ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Magrada Organic Cosmetics","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":48927701696839,"sku":"","price":13.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/magrada-volumizing-solid-conditioner-with-linden-flower-extract-50g-360749.png?v=1739897404"},{"product_id":"rhubarb-hair-mask-with-castor-oil-250-ml","title":"Magrada Moisturizing Hair Mask with Rhubarb Extract 250ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg class=\"alignnone wp-image-11509\" src=\"https:\/\/www.magrada.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/5-300x300.png\" alt=\"pure beauty global awards 2021\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\"\u003e\u003cimg class=\"alignnone wp-image-11514\" src=\"https:\/\/www.magrada.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/6-1-300x300.png\" alt=\"pure beauty global awards 2021\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\"\u003e\u003cimg class=\"alignnone wp-image-11524\" src=\"https:\/\/www.magrada.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/8-300x300.png\" alt=\"global green beauty awards 2021\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\"\u003e\u003cimg class=\"alignnone wp-image-11519\" src=\"https:\/\/www.magrada.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/7-300x300.png\" alt=\"buduaar beauty award 2022\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\"\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eVoluminous, shiny, healthy – we have created a professional hair care collection for you to enjoy beautiful salon hair every day.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe gold medal-winning (Pure Beauty Global Awards 2021 Winner) hair mask is designed for intensive nurturing and moisturising of dry and damaged hair.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe rhubarb hair mask with castor oil and macadamia oil pampers, revives, and smooths damaged hair. The vitality of the plants has a balancing and nurturing effect. The natural care improves the hair structure and reduces damage, adding a captivating shine to the hair.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe silky, creamy composition will give the hair a spring-like freshness and the juicy aroma of rhubarb.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eThanks to its anti-inflammatory and anti-bacterial properties, \u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003erhubarb root extract\u003c\/span\u003e soothes a sensitive and irritated scalp.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eMacadamia oil\u003c\/span\u003e is rich in fatty acids and potassium, which will make your hair stronger and easier to comb. Macadamia oil contains antioxidants which help the hair to recover from damaging environmental impacts.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eCastor oil\u003c\/span\u003e has an anti-microbial effect, which helps to reduce dandruff and other scalp issues deteriorating hair health. The vitamin E in the oil moisturises hair roots and gives the hair a healthy shine.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply the mask on damp hair after shampooing, starting from the tips. Leave in for 5–15 minutes, then rinse with plenty of water.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eStore at a temperature of 5 to 25 degrees. When storing, protect from direct sunlight. Do not store the product near heaters or other heat sources.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Cetearyl Alcohol, Cetrimonium Chloride, Behentrimonium Methosulfate, Macadamia Ternifolia (Macadamia) Seed Oil, Ricinus Communis (Castor) Seed Oil, Cetyl Alcohol, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Hydrolyzed Wheat Starch, Parfum, Butylene Glycol, Rheum Palmatum (Rhubarb) Root Extract, Triethanolamine, Phenoxyethanol, Ethylhexylglycerin\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIngredients of natural origin: 94,16%.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe list of ingredients may be changed. Please see the packaging for the updated and most accurate list of ingredients.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eparaben-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e sulphate-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e silicone-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e vegan \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e alcohol-free | EU allergen-free | cruelty-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e hand-made \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e with a minimal list of ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Magrada Organic Cosmetics","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":48927707627847,"sku":"","price":15.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/magrada-moisturizing-hair-mask-with-rhubarb-extract-250ml-9001472.png?v=1763665705"},{"product_id":"reise-leave-in-conditioner-50ml","title":"REISE Leave-In Conditioner 50ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePlant-sourced moisturizing ingredients, organic plant extract relieving sensitive discomfort, improve dry skin problems.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe plant oil repair formula is absorbed quickly into the hair without leaving a sticky feeling. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIt allows easy combing and leaves the hair light and refresh.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eRice Amino acid moisturizing formula increases hair moisture content. Liquid gold Argan Oil, Rice Bran and Camellia Oil repair damaged, fuzzy and split hairs, moisturizing hair and improve dryness restoring glow. Added vitamin B5 helps strengthen the hair and increase elasticity. Reproduces bright, smooth and elegant hair. Can be used on both wet and dry hair without rinsing out, suitable for all hair types. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCaprylhydroxamic Acid preservative, alcohol-free, and contains no animal derived or stimulating ingredients.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eAfter washing your hair, dry any excess water out and pour appropriate amount of hair oil to the palm of your hand. Apply evenly to damp hair for your hair to absorb, then dry your hair. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eStore in cool, dry place away from direct sunlight.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eArgania Spinosa Kernel Oil, Rice Bran Oil*, Rice Amino Acids, Camella Oleifera Seed Oil, Sea Salt Extract, Cetearyl Olivate, Citric Acid, Caprylic\/Capric Triglyceride, Sodium Anisate, Citrus Aurantium Dulcis Oil, Cymbopogon Flexuosus Oil(Cymbopogon Citratus\/Cymbopogon Citratus Leaf Oil, Panthenol, Tocopherol.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e*Ingredients from certified organic agriculture\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAnimal ingredients free | Silicone-free | Alcohol-free | Fragrance-free | No Parabens preservatives\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMade In Taiwan\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Reise","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49274438910279,"sku":null,"price":27.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/reise-leave-in-conditioner-50ml-937676.jpg?v=1739897350"},{"product_id":"bee-it-reconstruction-hair-mask-250ml-1","title":"BEE IT Reconstruction Hair Mask 200ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eA concentrated repairing post shampoo mask which gratifies for its immediate effectiveness. Gives strength and elasticity, deeply hydrating and nourishing for a healthy, luminous and plumped up hair.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Apply after shampooing to towel-dried hair. Leave on for 5-10 minutes, then comb and rinse. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Aqua, Behenamidopropyl dimethylamine, Cetearyl alcohol, Lactic acid, Phenoxyethanol, Parfum, Guar hydroxypropyltrimonium chloride, Tocopheryl acetate, Sorbitol, Ethylhexylglycerin, Tetrasodium glutamate diacetate, Olea europaea fruit oil*, Opuntia ficus-indica seed oil, Glycerin, Myrtus communis extract, Panthenol, Hamamelis virginiana leaf extract*, Mel*, Propolis, Retinyl palmitate, Limonene, Linalool, Sodium benzoate, Potassium sorbate.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e*Organic\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e100% Natural Ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eAnimal Friendly | No Paraffin | No Silicones | No Parabens | 100% Recyclable\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e“Less plastic is fantastic” packaging is using 70% less plastic compared to a normal bottle pack. Less bulk, being soft and doesn’t break, generates a better recycling chain and allows use of all its contents.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eBy purchasing BEE IT cosmetics  you contribute to the creation of new bee oasis. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eMade in Italy\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"BEE IT","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49354507583815,"sku":null,"price":14.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/bee-it-reconstruction-hair-mask-200ml-244590.jpg?v=1739897339"},{"product_id":"naif-2-in-1-shampoo-conditioner-for-kids-200ml","title":"NAIF 2-in-1 Shampoo \u0026 Conditioner for Kids 200ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e2-in-1 kids Shampoo \u0026amp; Conditioner for all hairtypes (long, short, thick or curly). The shampoo cleanses your hair while the anti-tangle formula ensures that the hair is soft and easy to comb through. Softens and detangles hair and hydrates with sunflower- and linseed oil. For all kids. Without SLES or microplastics.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMild, fruity scent developed for and by children.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eTake a coin-sized amount of Naif 2-in-1 Shampoo and Conditioner and massage into wet hair. Leave it in for a bit, rinse.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua\/Water, Coco-Glucoside, Sodium Coco-Sulfate, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Glycerin, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Gossypium Hirsutum (Cotton) Seed Extract, Panthenol, Pantolactone, Betaine, Inulin, Guar Hydroxypropyltrimonium Chloride, Glyceryl Oleate, Tocopherol, Hydrogenated Palm Glycerides Citrate, Sodium Levulinate, Sodium Anisate, Sodium Chloride, Fragrance, Citric Acid, Sodium Hydroxide\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTube made from bioplastic\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49445993644359,"sku":null,"price":11.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-2-in-1-shampoo-conditioner-for-kids-200ml-851648.png?v=1739897337"},{"product_id":"naif-softening-conditioner-for-kids-200ml","title":"NAIF Softening Conditioner for Kids 200ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eCurly hair, coarse hair, thick hair - Naïf's Kids Conditioner nourishes and softens the hair of our little ones and makes it easy to comb through. Thanks to the addition of cottonseed oil, the hair is not only cared for, but also frizz-free. Suitable for all hair types.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eRemoves tangles and moisturizes the hair with sunflower and linseed oil. No SLES and microplastics. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eMild and fruity fragrance - developed by and for kids.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eUse the conditioner after shampoo and apply from the ends only. Let it sit and rinse! You can use the conditioner after every wash.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Aqua\/Water, Cetearyl Alcohol, Glycerin, Glyceryl Stearate SE, Distearoylethyl Hydroxyethylmonium Methosulfate, Stearamidopropyl Dimethylamine, Gossypium Herbaceum (Cotton) Seed Oil, Panthenol, Pantolactone, Tocopherol, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil, Hydroxyethylcellulose, Behentrimonium Chloride, Dipropylene Glycol, Sodium Levulinate, Sodium Anisate, Fragrance, Citric Acid, Sodium Hydroxide\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eTube made from bioplastic\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49446052004167,"sku":null,"price":11.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-softening-conditioner-for-kids-200ml-924525.png?v=1739897345"},{"product_id":"naif-easy-styling-hair-lotion-for-baby-kids-150ml","title":"NAIF Easy Styling Hair Lotion for Baby \u0026 Kids 150ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eA hair lotion to tame and take care of wild kids hair. Naïf's Easy Styling Hair Lotion makes combing easier and reduces tangles and frizz for all hair types. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHair lotion with natural ingredients that doesn't make the hair greasy\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eSoftens knots and tangles in the hair and reduces frizz in curls\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eCan also be used with cradle cap\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eFor use on babies and children, for all hairtypes\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eDoes not contain microplastics, mineral oils, SLES or silicones\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eSpray on towel-dried hair from 30 cm away. Massage gently, comb through the hair and style. Suitable for daily use.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Aqua\/Water, Methylpropanediol, Caprylyl\/Capryl Glucoside, Glycerin, Gossypium Hirsutum (Cotton Seed) Extract, Caprylyl Glycol, Phenylpropanol, Inulin, Betaine, Sodium Cocoyl Glutamate, Glyceryl Caprylate, Polyglyceryl-6 Oleate, Sodium Surfactin, Parfum\/Fragrance (allergen-free), Lactic Acid, Citric Acid, Sodium Hydroxide\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eBottle made from recycled plastic\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49446066323783,"sku":null,"price":14.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-easy-styling-hair-lotion-for-baby-kids-150ml-404694.png?v=1739897336"},{"product_id":"nurme-lemongrass-conditioner-250ml","title":"NURME Lemongrass Conditioner 250ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eOur all-natural hair conditioners are rich in fatty acids and have a smoothing and moisturizing quality. It gives your hair shine and makes it softer to the touch. The conditioner gives a protective coating to the air follicles and therefore prevents hair breaking so easily.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe conditioner contains lemongrass essential oil, one of the most popular oils in Nurme’s range. Lemongrass shampoo and conditioner are also one of our customer favorites.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eAfter washing add a small amount of conditioner to your hair and leave it on for 1-2 minutes. For extra nourishment, gently massage some product on the scalp. Rinse with plenty of water.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003eThe conditioner is very thick which means it doesn’t take much. When the bottle is emptied to the last third, we recommend to add a little water to facilitate use.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Cetyl Alcohol**, Glycerin**, Behentrimonium Chloride*, Betaine**, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil*, Argania Spinosa Kernel Oil*, Panthenol*, Tocopherol**, Cymbopogon Citratus Leaf Oil*, Behenyl Alcohol**, Decyltetradecanol*, Sodium Benzoate**, Oleyl Erucate**, Potassium Sorbate**,Citric Acid, Geraniol***, Citral***. *Natural origin **Natural products approved ingredients ***Occurs naturally in essential oil\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e0% SLS | 0% SLES | 0% Parabens\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"Nurme","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49553859281223,"sku":null,"price":11.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/nurme-lemongrass-conditioner-250ml-730016.jpg?v=1739897241"},{"product_id":"nurme-rosemary-hair-conditioner-250ml","title":"NURME Rosemary Conditioner 250ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eOur all-natural hair conditioners are rich in fatty acids and have a smoothing and moisturizing quality. It gives your hair shine and makes it softer to the touch. The conditioner gives a protective coating to the air follicles and therefore prevents hair breakage.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eRosemary essential oil promotes hair growth, helps relieve dry skin problems and has anti-dandruff and anti-itch properties.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eAfter washing add a small amount of conditioner to your hair and leave it on for 1-2 minutes. For extra nourishment, gently massage some product on the scalp. Rinse with plenty of water.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003eThe conditioner is very thick which means it doesn’t take much. When the bottle is emptied to the last third, we recommend to add a little water to facilitate use.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Cetyl Alcohol*, Glycerin**, Behentrimonium Chloride*, Betaine**, Heliantus Annuus Seed Oil*, Argania Spinosa Kernel Oil*, Panthenol*, Tocopherol**, Rosmarinus Officinalis Leaf Oil*, Behenyl Alcohol**, Decyltetradecanol*, Sodium Benzoate**, Oleyl Erucate**, Potassium Sorbate**, Citric Acid, Limonene***. *Natural origin **Natural cosmetics approved ingredients ***Occurs naturally in essentail oils\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e0% SLS | 0% SLES | 0% Parabens\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"Nurme","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49553864130887,"sku":null,"price":11.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/nurme-rosemary-conditioner-250ml-490893.jpg?v=1739897238"},{"product_id":"nurme-lavender-hair-conditioner-250ml","title":"NURME Lavender Conditioner 250ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eOur all-natural hair conditioners are rich in fatty acids and have a smoothing and moisturizing quality. It gives your hair shine and makes it softer to the touch. The conditioner gives a protective coating to the air follicles and therefor preventing hair breakage.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eLavender essential oil is richly nourishing, moisturizes the scalp and hair, helps prevent hair loss, and improves scalp circulation, thereby promoting hair growth.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eAfter washing add a small amount of conditioner to your hair and leave it on for 1-2 minutes. For extra nourishment, gently massage some product on the scalp. Rinse with plenty of water.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003eThe conditioner is very thick which means it doesn’t take much. When the bottle is emptied to the last third, we recommend to add a little water to facilitate use.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Cetyl Alcohol**, Glycerin**, Behentrimonium Chloride*, Betaine**, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil*, Argania Spinosa Kernel Oil*, Panthenol*, Tocopherol**, Lavandula Angustifolia (Lavender) Flower Oil*, Behenyl Alcohol**, Decyltetradecanol*, Sodium Benzoate**, Oleyl Erucate**, Potassium Sorbate**, Citric Acid, Linalool***. \u003cem\u003e\u003c\/em\u003e*Natural origin **Natural products approved ingredients ***Occures naturally in essential oils\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e0% SLS | 0% SLES | 0% Parabens\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"Nurme","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49553876746567,"sku":null,"price":11.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/nurme-lavender-conditioner-250ml-812234.jpg?v=1739897248"},{"product_id":"nurme-ylang-ylang-conditioner-250ml","title":"NURME Ylang-Ylang Conditioner 250ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eOur all-natural hair conditioners are rich in fatty acids and have a smoothing and moisturizing quality. It gives your hair shine and makes it softer to the touch. The conditioner gives a protective coating to the air follicles and therefore prevents hair breakage.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eYlang-ylang essential oil is known as a good moisturizer and it also promotes hair regrowth. Ylang-ylang has a sweet floral scent and reminds you those warm summer days.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eAfter washing add a small amount of conditioner to your hair and leave it on for 1-2 minutes. For extra nourishment, gently massage some product on the scalp. Rinse with plenty of water.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003eThe conditioner is very thick which means it doesn’t take much. When the bottle is emptied to the last third, we recommend to add a little water to facilitate use.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Cetyl Alcohol**, Glycerin**, Behentrimonium Chloride*, Betaine**, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil*, Argania Spinosa Kernel Oil*, Panthenol*, Tocopherol**, Cananga Odorate Flower Oil*, Behenyl Alcohol**, Decyltetradecanol*, Sodium Benzoate**, Oleyl Erucate**, Potassium Sorbate**,Citric Acid, Linalool***. *Natural origin **Natural products approved ingredients ***Occurs naturally in essential oil\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cspan\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cspan\u003e0% SLS | 0% SLES | 0% Parabens\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"Nurme","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49553879531847,"sku":null,"price":11.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/nurme-ylang-ylang-conditioner-250ml-978051.jpg?v=1739897237"},{"product_id":"hoia-hydrating-hair-mist-100ml","title":"HOIA Hydrating Hair Mist 100ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePleasantly scented hydrating spray helps to keep hair healthy, strong and shiny. Spray contains locally sourced nettle extract and rice water to strengthen hair, plant-based keratin, deeply moisturizing hyaluronic acid and aloe, hair-softening seaweed extracts and plant hydrosols, nourishing oils and shine-enhancing essential oils.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Shake the bottle before use and spray an appropriate amount onto wet or dry hair. No need to rinse hair.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003e*Salvia Officinalis Distillate water, *Achillea Millefolium Distillate water, Oryza Sativa Seed water, Chodrus Crispus extract, Sargassum Fluitans\/Natans extract, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Crambe Abyssinica Seed oil, *Nigella Sativa Seed oil, Saccharomyces Ferment, Lactobacillus Ferment, Hydronated Sodium Hyaluronate, Glycerin, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf juice, Sodium Levulinate, Urtica Dioica Plant extract, Pentylene Glycol, Sodium Anisate, *Lavandula Angustifolia oil, *Pelargonium Graveolens oil, Citric Acid. **Citral, **Geraniol, **Linalool, **Limonene, **Citronellol. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e*Organic. **Natural components of essential oil\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHandmade in Saaremaa\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"HOIA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50324565688647,"sku":null,"price":23.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hoia-hydrating-hair-mist-100ml-963057.jpg?v=1739897245"},{"product_id":"vielo-organic-conditioner-250ml","title":"Vielö Organic Conditioner 250ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNourishing organic conditioner, specially designed to strengthen and moisturise damaged hair, leaving it soft and smooth.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCreated with organic whey (nourishing), soy extract (invigorating), wheat germ oil (protecting), organic extracts of lavender (soothing), sage (strengthening) and mallow (moisturising).\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSuitable for all hair types.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply after shampooing to wet hair. Massage gently into hair and on scalp. Rinse thoroughly.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003c\/span\u003eLactis Serum Proteinum**, Triticum Vulgare Germ Oil**, Polyglyceryl-3 Dicitrate\/Stearate*, Cetyl Alcohol*, Glycerin**, Aqua*, Betaine*, Citric Acid*, Xanthan Gum*, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Oil**, Tocopherol*, Salvia Officinalis Oil**, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil**, Potassium Sorbate, Citronellol**\/***, Pelargonium Graveolens Flower Oil**, Geraniol**\/***, Malva Sylvestris Flower Extract**, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Extract**, Glycine Soja Seed Extract*, Urtica Dioica Leaf Extract**, Rosmarinus Officinalis Leaf Extract**, Polyglyceryl-4 Caprate*, Salvia Officinalis Leaf Extract**, Sodium Lactate*, Sodium Benzoate.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e* from natural origin (99,8%)\u003cbr\u003e** certified organic (88,9%)\u003cbr\u003e*** from natural essential oils\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003eHandmade in Austria\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003eInspired by circular economy, Vielö refines a high-quality by-product of cheese production, liquid organic whey, and uses it to create certified organic and sustainable skin and body care products.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"vielö","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50901055078727,"sku":null,"price":32.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/vielo-organic-conditioner-250ml-654164.jpg?v=1739897176"},{"product_id":"madara-nourish-and-repair-conditioner-200ml","title":"MÁDARA Nourish and Repair conditioner 200ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003eDeeply nourish and repair dry, damaged hair with this rich and creamy conditioner. Formulated with Northern Nettle and Quince, it helps to prevent breakage and split ends for silkier and more healthy-looking hair.\u0026amp;nbsp; Plus, this conditioner is packaged in a 60% post-consumer recycled tube to reduce the volume of new plastic packaging made each year!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan style=\"font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif;\"\u003e​​\u003c\/span\u003eMassage into wet, clean hair. Leave in for 1-3 minutes, then rinse thoroughly with water. For best results use in combination with M\u003cspan style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Aptos; mso-hansi-font-family: Aptos; mso-bidi-font-family: Aptos;\"\u003eÁ\u003c\/span\u003eDARA Nourish and Repair Shampoo.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Cetearyl Alcohol, D-panthenol (Provitamin B5), Betaine, Glycerin, Behentrimonium Chloride, Distearoylethyl Dimonium Chloride, Persea Gratissima (Avocado) Oil, Tocopherol, Mica (CI 77019), Lactic Acid, Benzyl Alcohol, Aroma, CI 77891 (Titanium Dioxide), Sodium Benzoate, Pyrus Cydonia (Quince) Fruit Extract, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Urtica Dioica (Nettle) Leaf Extract, Potassium Sorbate, Limonene, Linalool, Citrus Aurantium Peel Oil\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003eCOSMOS ORGANIC certified\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003ePlease note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50917259739463,"sku":null,"price":14.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-nourish-and-repair-conditioner-200ml-492639.jpg?v=1739897193"},{"product_id":"madara-colour-and-shine-conditioner-200ml","title":"MÁDARA Colour and Shine conditioner 200ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eDeeply nourish and protect treated and coloured hair with this colour preserving conditioner. Formulated with enriching Northern Linseed, Horse Chestnut and Plantain, it deeply nourishes and protects treated and coloured hair. Helps to smooth frizz and maintain vibrancy of hair colour for shinier, silky smooth and easier to style hair. Plus, this conditioner is packaged in a 60% post-consumer recycled tube to reduce the volume of new plastic packaging made each year!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Massage into wet, clean hair. Leave in for 1-3 minutes, then thoroughly with water. For best results use in combination with MÁDARA Colour And Shine Shampoo.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Cetearyl Alcohol, Betaine, Glycerin, Behentrimonium Chloride, D-panthenol (Provitamin B5), Mica (CI 77019), Lactic Acid, Benzyl Alcohol, Aroma, CI 77891 (Titanium Dioxide), Sodium Benzoate, Linum Usitatissimum (Linseed) Seed Extract, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Potassium Sorbate, Aesculus Hippocastanum (Horse Chestnut) Seed Extract, Plantago Major (Plantain) Leaf Extract, Limonene, Linalool, Citrus Aurantium Peel Oil\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCOSMOS ORGANIC certified\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePlease note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50917317706055,"sku":null,"price":14.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-colour-and-shine-conditioner-200ml-869960.jpg?v=1739897158"},{"product_id":"madara-gloss-and-vibrancy-conditioner-200ml","title":"MÁDARA Gloss and Vibrancy conditioner 200ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eDeeply nourish and strengthen the hair with this shine enhancing conditioner, formulated with Northern Birch and Cranberry. After use, hair becomes silky smooth, shinier and easier to style. Plus, this conditioner is packaged in a 60% post-consumer recycled tube to reduce the volume of new plastic packaging made each year!\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif;\"\u003e​​​\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eMassage into wet, clean hair. Leave in for 1-3 minutes, then thoroughly with water. For best results use in combination with MÁDARA Gloss And Vibrancy Shampoo.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Aqua, Cetearyl Alcohol, Betaine, Glycerin, Distearoylethyl Dimonium Chloride, Mica (CI 77019), D-panthenol (Provitamin B5), Lactic Acid, Benzyl Alcohol, Aroma, CI 77891 (Titanium Dioxide), Sodium Benzoate, Betula Alba (Birch) Leaf Extract, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Vaccinium Macrocarpon (Cranberry) Fruit Extract, Potassium Sorbate, Limonene, Linalool, Citrus Aurantium Peel Oil\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eCOSMOS ORGANIC certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003ePlease note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50917339889991,"sku":null,"price":14.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-gloss-and-vibrancy-conditioner-200ml-676619.jpg?v=1739897175"},{"product_id":"madara-feed-repair-dry-rescue-hair-mask-180ml","title":"MÁDARA FEED Repair \u0026 Dry Rescue hair mask 180ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003eDeeply nourish your hair with this exceptional oil blend and fungi-based restructure mask that also prevents fiber damage , preserves colour and softens the hair.  Strengthens the lipid matrix and improves protection against mechanical damage and heat appliance to ensure silky smooth high-shine hair for days.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif;\"\u003e​​​​\u003c\/span\u003eApply to clean, damp hair lengths and ends. Leave in for 5–10 minutes and rinse out thoroughly.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/b\u003e Cantharellus cibarius (chanterelle) extract, Cetearyl Alcohol, Distearoylethyl Dimonium Chloride, Glycerin, Brassica Alcohol, PCA Glyceryl Oleate, Sodium PCA, Brassicyl Isoleucinate Esylate, Lactic Acid, Aroma, Cocos Nucifera (Coconut) Oil, Xylitylglucoside, Butylene Glycol, Guar Hydroxypropyltrimonium Chloride, Benzyl Alcohol, Anhydroxylitol, Persea Gratissima (Avocado) Oil, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Sodium Benzoate, Xylitol, Hydrolyzed Keratin, Potassium Sorbate, Ascorbyl Palmitate, Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter, Oenothera Biennis (Evening Primrose) Oil, Prunus Amygdalus Dulcis (Sweet Almond) Oil, Tocopherol, Crambe Maritima (Sea Kale) Leaf Extract, Leuconostoc\/Radish Root Ferment Filtrate, Linalool, Limonene, Citrus Aurantium Peel Oil, Juniperus Virginiana Oil, Benzyl Salicylate\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003eCOSMOS ORGANIC certified\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003ePlease note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50917384552775,"sku":null,"price":23.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-feed-repair-dry-rescue-hair-mask-180ml-298387.png?v=1740808672"},{"product_id":"blokzeep-conditioner-bar-argan-60g","title":"Blokzeep Conditioner Bar Argan 60g","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe Argan conditioner bar is especially for dry hair. Argan oil is a rich mix that includes fatty acids, antioxidants and vitamin E. This composition has the property of penetrating relatively deep into the hair, making the hair more flexible. In addition, linoleic acid is an important component in Argan oil, which creates a protective layer that makes your hair retain moisture better and make it shine. Finally, the antioxidants in Argan oil provide external protection.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis Argan conditioner bar is sustainable for three reasons:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eLess water: A normal bottle of conditioner contains 80% water, which must be transported every time. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMore efficient use: A conditioner block lasts 3 times as long as a normal bottle of conditioner. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePlastic-free packaging\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis Conditioner bar Argan is handmade within Europe and transported to the Netherlands in a CO2 neutral manner. Packaging is 100% plastic-free.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eAfter washing your hair with a shampoo, massage the conditioner gently into wet ends and then rinse.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eSodium Coco-Sulfate, Cetearyl Alcohol, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter, Glyceryl Stearate SE, Sea Salt, Theobroma Cacao Seed Butter, Parfum, Argania Spinosa Kernel Oil, Mentha Piperita Leaf Extract, Tilia Cordata Extract, Аloe Barbadensis Extract, Phenoxyethanol, Tocopherol (Vitamin E), Linalool, Coumarin, Benzyl Alcohol, Limonene\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e cruelty-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e handmade\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Blokzeep","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50938784383303,"sku":null,"price":9.99,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/blokzeep-conditioner-bar-argan-60g-519679.jpg?v=1739897153"},{"product_id":"blokzeep-conditioner-bar-olive-60g","title":"Blokzeep Conditioner Bar Olive 60g","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eOlive has been known for centuries as a fantastic conditioner for your hair. This powerful and natural ingredient, rich in fatty acids and antioxidant vitamin E, has an intensely nourishing and softening effect without weighing the hair. In addition to Olive, this conditioner bar also contains Shea Butter. This is rich in antioxidants that regulate the moisture balance of your skin and hair and thus has a moisturizing and soothing effect. This combination of ingredients is ideal nutrition for your hair!\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis Olive conditioner bar is sustainable for three reasons:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eLess water: A normal bottle of conditioner contains 80% water, which must be transported every time. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMore efficient use: A conditioner block lasts 3 times as long as a normal bottle of shampoo. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePlastic-free packaging\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis Conditioner bar Olive is handmade within Europe and transported to the Netherlands in a CO2 neutral manner. Packaging is 100% plastic-free.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eAfter washing your hair with a shampoo, massage the conditioner gently into wet ends and then rinse.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eSodium Coco-Sulfate, Cetearyl Alcohol, Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Glyceryl Stearate SE, Sea Salt, Olea Europaea (Olive) Fruit Oil, Parfum, Mentha Piperita Extract, Calendula Officinalis Extract, Phenoxyethanol, Tocopherol (Vitamin E), Benzyl Benzoate, Linalool, Benzyl Salicylate, Limonene, Hydroxycitronellal, Citronellol\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e cruelty-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e handmade\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Blokzeep","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50938816299335,"sku":null,"price":9.99,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/blokzeep-conditioner-bar-olive-60g-613662.jpg?v=1739897167"},{"product_id":"blokzeep-conditioner-bar-avocado-60g","title":"Blokzeep Conditioner Bar Avocado 60g","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSpecially for dry \u0026amp; damaged hair. The good fats in Avocado have many applications, including as a conditioner. The Avocado oil in this conditioner bar has a moisturizing effect on dry hair, giving it a beautiful shine. In addition to Avocado, this conditioner bar also contains Shea Butter and Mango Butter, two ingredients that are also known for their good properties. Shea Butter is rich in antioxidants that regulate the moisture balance of your skin and hair and therefore has a moisturizing and soothing effect. Mango butter has a similar structure to Shea Butter and also contains many antioxidants. It has a restorative effect and strengthens your hair roots. This combination of ingredients is ideal nutrition for your hair!\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis Avocado conditioner bar is sustainable for three reasons:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eLess water: A normal bottle of conditioner contains 80% water, which must be transported every time. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMore efficient use: A conditioner block lasts 3 times as long as a normal bottle of conditioner \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePlastic-free packaging\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis Conditioner bar Avocado is handmade within Europe and transported to the Netherlands in a CO2 neutral manner. Packaging is 100% plastic-free.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eAfter washing your hair with a shampoo, massage the conditioner gently into wet ends and then rinse.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eSodium Coco-Sulfate, Cetearyl Alcohol, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter, Glyceryl Stearate SE, Sea Salt, Cocos Nucifera Oil, Parfum, Persea Gratissima (Avocado) Oil, Mangifera Indica Seed (Mango) Butter, Phenoxyethanol, Tocopherol (Vitamin E), Benzyl Benzoate, Hexyl Cinnamal\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e cruelty-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e handmade\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Blokzeep","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50938829570375,"sku":null,"price":9.99,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/blokzeep-conditioner-bar-avocado-60g-193510.jpg?v=1739897160"},{"product_id":"luuv-natural-kids-detangling-spray-100ml","title":"LUUV Natural Kids Detangling Spray 100ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eCertified with the globally recognized ECOCERT\/COSMOS certification, this spray is a game-changer for your little one’s hair care routine. It’s time to say goodbye to stubborn tangles and hello to hassle-free styling!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eLUUV Detangle spray is specially formulated to tame even the most stubborn knots, leaving your little one’s hair silky smooth, strong, and oh-so-shiny! And let’s not forget the delightful scent! Detangling spray comes with a mouthwatering juicy pear scent that kids absolutely adore. Plus, you can rest easy knowing that the scent is naturally derived and free from any allergens. Your little one’s hair is in good hands. And now that your little one’s hair is tangle-free, it’s time to explore a whole new world of hairstyles! From cute pigtails to stylish braids, this spray opens up endless possibilities for your child’s hair adventures.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNatural and allergen-free\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFresh pear scent\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDoes not irritate skin\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eECOCERT\/COSMOS certified\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNatural origin 99,76%\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural | cruelty free | sustainable | vegan | certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe product is made in Estonia\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eShake the bottle before use. Spray the conditioner on the hair, let it work for a few moments and comb through the hair. Can be used both on wet hair after washing and on dry hair daily.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Cetearyl Alcohol, Lecithin, Sodium Cetearyl Sulfate, Olus Oil, Propanediol, Betaine, Coconut Alkanes, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Citric Acid, Aroma\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LUUV","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51115375034695,"sku":null,"price":14.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/luuv-natural-kids-detangling-spray-100ml-412749.png?v=1740891417"},{"product_id":"luuv-natural-volumizing-seabuckthorn-conditioner-200ml","title":"LUUV Natural Volumizing Seabuckthorn Conditioner 200ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNatural sea buckthorn conditioner is suitable for normal\/oily hair, it gives the hair softness, volume and shine. Sea buckthorn and castor oils strengthen the hair, help to prevent hair splitting and stimulate hair growth. Wheat protein makes the hair stronger and increases volume and elasticity. Provitamin B5 makes the hair easy to comb and protects from heat treatment. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003esuitable for all hair types, including oily hair\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003egives hair fluffiness and shine\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003emoisturizes and strengthens the hair\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ewith a citrus scent\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural | cruelty free | sustainable | vegan \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe product is made in Estonia\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply the conditioner on your hair after shampooing, starting from the tips. Leave in for 2–3 minutes, then rinse with plenty of water.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Coco-Glucoside, Betaine, Citric Acid, Xanthan Gum, Hippophae Rhamnoides (Sea Buckthorn) oil, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, PCA Glyceryl Oleate, Citrus Reticulata (Mandarin oil), Citrus Aurantium Dulcis (Orange) Oil, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Parfum, Limonene\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LUUV","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51115401118023,"sku":null,"price":11.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/luuv-natural-volumizing-seabuckthorn-conditioner-200ml-722591.png?v=1740891411"},{"product_id":"luuv-natural-caring-conditioner-with-plum-oil-200ml","title":"LUUV Natural Caring Conditioner With Plum Oil 200ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMaintained hair every day! Natural conditioner enriched with plum oil is perfect for daily use on all hair types. Cold-pressed plum oil moisturizes hair, restores hair ends and protects against heat treatment. The mixture of natural oils, proteins and active substances provides everything necessary for hair to be strong and shiny. Also suitable for colored hair.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli id=\"tw-target-text\" class=\"tw-data-text tw-text-large tw-ta\" dir=\"ltr\" data-placeholder=\"Tõlge\" aria-label=\"Tõlgitud tekst\" data-ved=\"2ahUKEwiX3-GDwdqGAxV6PhAIHYrmHigQ3ewLegQIBRAU\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"Y2IQFc\" lang=\"en\"\u003esuitable for all hair types, including dyed hair\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"tw-data-text tw-text-large tw-ta\" dir=\"ltr\" data-placeholder=\"Tõlge\" aria-label=\"Tõlgitud tekst\" data-ved=\"2ahUKEwiX3-GDwdqGAxV6PhAIHYrmHigQ3ewLegQIBRAU\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"Y2IQFc\" lang=\"en\"\u003ecaring and softening effect\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"tw-data-text tw-text-large tw-ta\" dir=\"ltr\" data-placeholder=\"Tõlge\" aria-label=\"Tõlgitud tekst\" data-ved=\"2ahUKEwiX3-GDwdqGAxV6PhAIHYrmHigQ3ewLegQIBRAU\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"Y2IQFc\" lang=\"en\"\u003emoisturizes and protects hair\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"tw-data-text tw-text-large tw-ta\" dir=\"ltr\" data-placeholder=\"Tõlge\" aria-label=\"Tõlgitud tekst\" data-ved=\"2ahUKEwiX3-GDwdqGAxV6PhAIHYrmHigQ3ewLegQIBRAU\"\u003e\n\u003cspan class=\"Y2IQFc\" lang=\"en\"\u003eprotects hair from heat treatment\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural | cruelty free | sustainable | vegan | paraben free\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe product is made in Estonia\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply the conditioner on your hair after shampooing, starting from the tips. Leave in for 2–3 minutes, then rinse with plenty of water.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Distearoylethyl Dimonium Chloride, Cetearyl Alcohol, Glycerin, Cetyl alcohol, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice, Betaine, PCA Glyceryl Oleate, Prunus Domestica (Plum) Seed oil, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Guar Hydroxypropyltrimonium Chloride, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Citric Acid, Cymbopogon Martini (Palmarosa) oil, Parfum, Geraniol\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LUUV","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51115415961927,"sku":null,"price":11.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/luuv-natural-caring-conditioner-with-plum-oil-200ml-901624.png?v=1740891410"},{"product_id":"luuv-natural-softening-protecting-honey-conditioner-200ml","title":"LUUV Natural Softening \u0026 Protecting Honey Conditioner 200ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNatural honey conditioner makes the hair soft and easy to comb, restoring damaged hair ends. Organic honey extract makes the hair silky and protects from environmental effects. Organic barley extract stimulates hair growth and gives shine. Wheat protein strengthens the hair and increases elasticity. Also suitable for colored hair.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003esuitable for all hair types, including dyed hair\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ewith a softening and protective effect\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003egives hair softness\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eimproves hair structure and strengthens hair\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ewith a honey-sweet smell\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural | cruelty free | sustainable \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe product is made in Estonia\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply the conditioner on your hair after shampooing, starting from the tips. Leave in for 2–3 minutes, then rinse with plenty of water.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Distearoylethyl Dimonium Chloride, Cetearyl Alcohol, Glycerin, Cocos Nucifera, Cetyl alcohol, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf juice, Betaine, Ricinus Communis Seed (Castor) Oil, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil, Propolis (Bee glue) extract, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Hordeum Vulgare (Barlay sprouts) Extract, Hippophae Rhamnoides (Sea Buckthorn) oil, PCA Glyceryl Oleate, Panthenol, Guar Hydroxypropyltrimonium Chloride, Coco-Glucoside, Glyceryl Oleate, Citric Acid, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Parfum  \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LUUV","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51115427070279,"sku":null,"price":11.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/luuv-natural-softening-protecting-honey-conditioner-200ml-904989.png?v=1740891412"},{"product_id":"magrada-hair-stimulating-conditioner-with-linden-flower-extract-travel-size-100ml","title":"Magrada Hair Stimulating Conditioner with Linden Flower Extract Travel Size 100ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eEnjoy midsummer moments all year round. This conditioner is characterised by a composition of efficient Nordic plants which supports and accelerates natural hair growth. The silky, creamy composition of the conditioner spreads evenly on the hair, leaving behind a slightly honey-like aroma – like a warm July night.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe Nordic birch extract moisturises and softens the hair, making it easy to comb. The organic aloe extract has an calming effect on the scalp and prevents drying of the tips. The composition of plant extracts gives the hair a healthy shine, protects it from heat treatment, and preserves the pigmentation of the hair follicles, helping the hair to remain lively and elastic. The light conditioner is suitable for the entire family for daily use.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eNordic linden flower extract \u003c\/span\u003ehas a moisturising and softening effect suitable for a sensitive or irritated scalp.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eThe organic Nordic birch extract \u003c\/span\u003estimulates the circulation in the scalp and strengthens the roots, thereby accelerating natural hair growth.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eThe organic aloe extract \u003c\/span\u003ehas a deeply calming and moisturising effect on the skin. Aloe is well-known for its rich vitamin A, C, and E, folic acid, and collagen content.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply the conditioner on your hair after shampooing, starting from the tips. Leave in for 2–3 minutes, then rinse with plenty of water. The conditioner is suitable for daily use.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eStore at a temperature of 5 to 25 degrees. When storing, protect from direct sunlight. Do not store the product near heaters or other heat sources.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Cetearyl Alcohol, Cetrimonium Chloride, Glycerin, Behentrimonium Methosulfate, Parfum, Cetyl Alcohol, Betula Alba (Birch) Leaf Exract*, Aloe Barbadensis (Aloe Vera) Extract*, Butylene Glycol, Alcohol, Tilia Cordata (Linden Flower) Extract, Phenoxyethanol, Ethylhexylglycerin, Potassium Sorbate, Sodium Benzoate, Hexyl Cinnamal, Geraniol\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e*COSMOS Certified Organic Ingredient\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIngredients of natural origin: 92,77%.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe list of ingredients may be changed. Please see the packaging for the updated and most accurate list of ingredients.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eparaben-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e sulphate-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e silicone-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e vegan\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e | cruelty-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e hand-made \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e with a minimal list of ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Magrada Organic Cosmetics","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51335078740295,"sku":null,"price":8.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/magrada-hair-stimulating-conditioner-with-linden-flower-extract-travel-size-100ml-426881.png?v=1743213039"},{"product_id":"magrada-moisturizing-hair-mask-with-rhubarb-extract-travel-size-100-ml","title":"Magrada Moisturizing Hair Mask with Rhubarb Extract Travel Size 100ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eVoluminous, shiny, healthy – we have created a professional hair care collection for you to enjoy beautiful salon hair every day.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe gold medal-winning (Pure Beauty Global Awards 2021 Winner) hair mask is designed for intensive nurturing and moisturising of dry and damaged hair.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe rhubarb hair mask with castor oil and macadamia oil pampers, revives, and smooths damaged hair. The vitality of the plants has a balancing and nurturing effect. The natural care improves the hair structure and reduces damage, adding a captivating shine to the hair.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe silky, creamy composition will give the hair a spring-like freshness and the juicy aroma of rhubarb.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eThanks to its anti-inflammatory and anti-bacterial properties, \u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003erhubarb root extract\u003c\/span\u003e soothes a sensitive and irritated scalp.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eMacadamia oil\u003c\/span\u003e is rich in fatty acids and potassium, which will make your hair stronger and easier to comb. Macadamia oil contains antioxidants which help the hair to recover from damaging environmental impacts.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eCastor oil\u003c\/span\u003e has an anti-microbial effect, which helps to reduce dandruff and other scalp issues deteriorating hair health. The vitamin E in the oil moisturises hair roots and gives the hair a healthy shine.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply the mask on damp hair after shampooing, starting from the tips. Leave in for 5–15 minutes, then rinse with plenty of water.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eStore at a temperature of 5 to 25 degrees. When storing, protect from direct sunlight. Do not store the product near heaters or other heat sources.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Cetearyl Alcohol, Cetrimonium Chloride, Behentrimonium Methosulfate, Macadamia Ternifolia (Macadamia) Seed Oil, Ricinus Communis (Castor) Seed Oil, Cetyl Alcohol, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Hydrolyzed Wheat Starch, Parfum, Butylene Glycol, Rheum Palmatum (Rhubarb) Root Extract, Triethanolamine, Phenoxyethanol, Ethylhexylglycerin\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIngredients of natural origin: 94,16%.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe list of ingredients may be changed. Please see the packaging for the updated and most accurate list of ingredients.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eparaben-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e sulphate-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e silicone-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e vegan \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e alcohol-free | EU allergen-free | cruelty-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e hand-made \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e with a minimal list of ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Magrada Organic Cosmetics","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51335117537607,"sku":null,"price":10.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/magrada-moisturizing-hair-mask-with-rhubarb-extract-travel-size-100ml-344835.png?v=1743213039"},{"product_id":"magrada-hair-stimulating-conditioner-with-linden-flower-extract-refill-500ml","title":"Magrada Hair Stimulating Conditioner with Linden Flower Extract Refill 500ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eEnjoy midsummer moments all year round. This conditioner is characterised by a composition of efficient Nordic plants which supports and accelerates natural hair growth. The silky, creamy composition of the conditioner spreads evenly on the hair, leaving behind a slightly honey-like aroma – like a warm July night.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe Nordic birch extract moisturises and softens the hair, making it easy to comb. The organic aloe extract has an calming effect on the scalp and prevents drying of the tips. The composition of plant extracts gives the hair a healthy shine, protects it from heat treatment, and preserves the pigmentation of the hair follicles, helping the hair to remain lively and elastic. The light conditioner is suitable for the entire family for daily use.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eNordic linden flower extract \u003c\/span\u003ehas a moisturising and softening effect suitable for a sensitive or irritated scalp.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eThe organic Nordic birch extract \u003c\/span\u003estimulates the circulation in the scalp and strengthens the roots, thereby accelerating natural hair growth.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eThe organic aloe extract \u003c\/span\u003ehas a deeply calming and moisturising effect on the skin. Aloe is well-known for its rich vitamin A, C, and E, folic acid, and collagen content.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply the conditioner on your hair after shampooing, starting from the tips. Leave in for 2–3 minutes, then rinse with plenty of water. The conditioner is suitable for daily use.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eStore at a temperature of 5 to 25 degrees. When storing, protect from direct sunlight. Do not store the product near heaters or other heat sources.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Cetearyl Alcohol, Cetrimonium Chloride, Glycerin, Behentrimonium Methosulfate, Parfum, Cetyl Alcohol, Betula Alba (Birch) Leaf Exract*, Aloe Barbadensis (Aloe Vera) Extract*, Butylene Glycol, Alcohol, Tilia Cordata (Linden Flower) Extract, Phenoxyethanol, Ethylhexylglycerin, Potassium Sorbate, Sodium Benzoate, Hexyl Cinnamal, Geraniol\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e*COSMOS Certified Organic Ingredient\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIngredients of natural origin: 92,77%.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe list of ingredients may be changed. Please see the packaging for the updated and most accurate list of ingredients.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eparaben-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e sulphate-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e silicone-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e vegan\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e | cruelty-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e hand-made \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e with a minimal list of ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Magrada Organic Cosmetics","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51335155482951,"sku":null,"price":22.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/magrada-hair-stimulating-conditioner-with-linden-flower-extract-refill-500ml-520987.png?v=1743213044"},{"product_id":"magrada-moisturizing-hair-mask-with-rhubarb-extract-refill-100ml","title":"Magrada Moisturizing Hair Mask with Rhubarb Extract Refill 500ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eVoluminous, shiny, healthy – we have created a professional hair care collection for you to enjoy beautiful salon hair every day.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe gold medal-winning (Pure Beauty Global Awards 2021 Winner) hair mask is designed for intensive nurturing and moisturising of dry and damaged hair.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe rhubarb hair mask with castor oil and macadamia oil pampers, revives, and smooths damaged hair. The vitality of the plants has a balancing and nurturing effect. The natural care improves the hair structure and reduces damage, adding a captivating shine to the hair.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe silky, creamy composition will give the hair a spring-like freshness and the juicy aroma of rhubarb.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eThanks to its anti-inflammatory and anti-bacterial properties, \u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003erhubarb root extract\u003c\/span\u003e soothes a sensitive and irritated scalp.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eMacadamia oil\u003c\/span\u003e is rich in fatty acids and potassium, which will make your hair stronger and easier to comb. Macadamia oil contains antioxidants which help the hair to recover from damaging environmental impacts.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eCastor oil\u003c\/span\u003e has an anti-microbial effect, which helps to reduce dandruff and other scalp issues deteriorating hair health. The vitamin E in the oil moisturises hair roots and gives the hair a healthy shine.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply the mask on damp hair after shampooing, starting from the tips. Leave in for 5–15 minutes, then rinse with plenty of water.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eStore at a temperature of 5 to 25 degrees. When storing, protect from direct sunlight. Do not store the product near heaters or other heat sources.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Cetearyl Alcohol, Cetrimonium Chloride, Behentrimonium Methosulfate, Macadamia Ternifolia (Macadamia) Seed Oil, Ricinus Communis (Castor) Seed Oil, Cetyl Alcohol, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Hydrolyzed Wheat Starch, Parfum, Butylene Glycol, Rheum Palmatum (Rhubarb) Root Extract, Triethanolamine, Phenoxyethanol, Ethylhexylglycerin\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIngredients of natural origin: 94,16%.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe list of ingredients may be changed. Please see the packaging for the updated and most accurate list of ingredients.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eparaben-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e sulphate-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e silicone-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e vegan \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e alcohol-free | EU allergen-free | cruelty-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e hand-made \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e with a minimal list of ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Magrada Organic Cosmetics","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51335181631815,"sku":null,"price":30.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/magrada-moisturizing-hair-mask-with-rhubarb-extract-refill-500ml-702844.png?v=1743213040"},{"product_id":"luuv-natural-conditioner-for-kids-200ml","title":"LUUV Natural Conditioner For Kids 200ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eThis enchanting conditioner deeply moisturizes, nourishes, and protects the hair, leaving it irresistibly shiny. LUUV children’s hair conditioner is certified with the prestigious ECOCERT\/COSMOS eco-certificate.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSay goodbye to tangles and hello to effortlessly smooth and manageable hair! Conditioner strengthens hair from roots to ends, making it easy to comb and wonderfully lightweight. Infused with natural oils and betaine, it deeply moisturizes and enhances the overall health and beauty of the hair. And let’s not forget about that enchanting vanilla aroma! It’s derived from natural sources and is completely allergen-free. If your little one dreams of becoming the next Rapunzel with long, flowing locks, LUUV natural conditioner for kids is the perfect choice!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNatural and allergen-free\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSweet vanilla scent\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDoes not irritate skin\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eECOCERT\/COSMOS certified\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNatural origin 98,72%\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural | cruelty free | sustainable | vegan | certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe product is made in Estonia\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e  Use the conditioner after shampoo and apply from the ends only. Let it sit and rinse! You can use the conditioner after every wash.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Aqua, Cetearyl Alcohol, Lecithin, Sodium Cetearyl Sulfate, Olus Oil, Cetyl Alcohol, Betaine, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Citric Acid, Aroma\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LUUV","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52138032202055,"sku":null,"price":11.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/luuv-natural-conditioner-for-kids-200ml-2844222.jpg?v=1756222791"},{"product_id":"bee-it-reconstruction-hair-mask-50ml","title":"BEE IT Reconstruction Hair Mask 50ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eA concentrated repairing post shampoo mask which gratifies for its immediate effectiveness. Gives strength and elasticity, deeply hydrating and nourishing for a healthy, luminous and plumped up hair.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Apply after shampooing to towel-dried hair. Leave on for 5-10 minutes, then comb and rinse. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Aqua, Behenamidopropyl dimethylamine, Cetearyl alcohol, Lactic acid, Phenoxyethanol, Parfum, Guar hydroxypropyltrimonium chloride, Tocopheryl acetate, Sorbitol, Ethylhexylglycerin, Tetrasodium glutamate diacetate, Olea europaea fruit oil*, Opuntia ficus-indica seed oil, Glycerin, Myrtus communis extract, Panthenol, Hamamelis virginiana leaf extract*, Mel*, Propolis, Retinyl palmitate, Limonene, Linalool, Sodium benzoate, Potassium sorbate.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e*Organic\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e100% Natural Ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eAnimal Friendly | No Paraffin | No Silicones | No Parabens | 100% Recyclable\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e“Less plastic is fantastic” packaging is using 70% less plastic compared to a normal bottle pack. Less bulk, being soft and doesn’t break, generates a better recycling chain and allows use of all its contents.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eBy purchasing BEE IT cosmetics  you contribute to the creation of new bee oasis. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eMade in Italy\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"BEE IT","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52138364764487,"sku":null,"price":4.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/bee-it-reconstruction-hair-mask-200ml-244590.jpg?v=1739897339"},{"product_id":"bee-it-reconstruction-hair-mask-50ml-copy","title":"BEE IT Reconstruction Hair Mask 1000ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eA concentrated repairing post shampoo mask which gratifies for its immediate effectiveness. Gives strength and elasticity, deeply hydrating and nourishing for a healthy, luminous and plumped up hair.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Apply after shampooing to towel-dried hair. Leave on for 5-10 minutes, then comb and rinse. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Aqua, Behenamidopropyl dimethylamine, Cetearyl alcohol, Lactic acid, Phenoxyethanol, Parfum, Guar hydroxypropyltrimonium chloride, Tocopheryl acetate, Sorbitol, Ethylhexylglycerin, Tetrasodium glutamate diacetate, Olea europaea fruit oil*, Opuntia ficus-indica seed oil, Glycerin, Myrtus communis extract, Panthenol, Hamamelis virginiana leaf extract*, Mel*, Propolis, Retinyl palmitate, Limonene, Linalool, Sodium benzoate, Potassium sorbate.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e*Organic\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e100% Natural Ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eAnimal Friendly | No Paraffin | No Silicones | No Parabens | 100% Recyclable\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eBy purchasing BEE IT cosmetics  you contribute to the creation of new bee oasis. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eMade in Italy\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"BEE IT","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52143566651719,"sku":null,"price":46.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/bee-it-reconstruction-hair-mask-1000ml-6779386.png?v=1756222787"},{"product_id":"hoia-natural-conditioner-rapuntsel-290ml","title":"HOIA Natural Conditioner Rapuntsel 290ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eOrganic Conditioner contains lots on useful fatty acids that moisturize and nourish you hair. The hair conditior is enriched with rhamnoides extract which strengthens the hair and adds shine. Its rich complex of essential oils helps to stimulate hair growth and imporves blood circulation to the scalp.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSuitable for all hair types, this natural conditioner is free from parabens, silicones, sulfates, and synthetic preservatives, making it an excellent choice for those seeking gentle yet effective hair care.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply to wet hair, massaging gently from roots to ends. Leave it on for a few minutes, then rinse thoroughly. For intensive care, use it as a deep-conditioning hair mask by leaving it on longer before rinsing to provide extra nourishment and hydration.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Cetyl alcohol, Cetrimonium Chloride, *Cocos Nucifera oil, *Hippophae Rhanoides Extract, *Pelargonium Graveolens Flower oil, *Lavandula Angustifolia Flower oil, *Mentha Piperita Leaf oil, *Juniperus Communis Fruit oil, *Citrus Aurantifolia Flower oil, *Rosmarinus Officinails Leaf oil, *Cymbopogon Flexuosus Leaf oil, Tocopherol, Glyceryl stearate, Citric acid, Benzyl alcohol, Phenoxyethanol \u0026amp; Ethylhexylglycerin, **Citral, **Citronellol, **Geraniol, **Limonene, **Linalool. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e*From organic farming\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e**Natural components of essential oils\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"HOIA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52247240999239,"sku":null,"price":29.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hoia-natural-conditioner-rapuntsel-290ml-4153801.jpg?v=1756718906"},{"product_id":"nurme-balneological-peat-strenghtening-conditioner-250ml","title":"NURME Balneological Peat Strenghtening Conditioner 250ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis 100% natural peat conditioner offers your hair the ultimate care by deeply moisturizing and strengthening it. Its unique ingredients help prevent breakage and split ends, leaving your hair soft, smooth, and healthy. Nurme’s peat conditioner restores your hair’s natural shine and elasticity, delivering perfect care with every wash. It is perfect for revitalizing dry and damaged hair, restoring essential moisture and vitality.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eKey Ingredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eBalneological Peat\u003c\/span\u003e is rich in nutrients and minerals that nourish and strengthen hair ends. It helps restore elasticity and resilience, making hair more durable and vibrant.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eAloe Vera\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003eis renowned for its deeply hydrating and soothing properties. This natural ingredient keeps hair ends soft and silky, enhances shine, and reduces dryness.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eJojoba Oil\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003eis a natural moisturizer that deeply nourishes the hair and restores its natural moisture balance. It prevents breakage and split ends, giving hair strength and elasticity.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eCoconut Oil\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003enourishes hair deeply, improving its structure and promoting a healthier appearance. It smooths the hair and reduces dryness, leaving it soft and manageable.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eProvitamin B5\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003epenetrates the hair shaft, strengthening and restoring the hair from within. It reduces breakage and split ends while adding shine and making hair easy to comb.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eJuniper Essential Oil\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003eenhances the natural shine and softness of hair. Its smoothing effect protects against external damage and keeps hair ends well-maintained. It also amplifies the benefits of peat.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eWash your hair thoroughly with Nurme Peat shampoo. Then apply a small amount of conditioner to clean hair ends and leave it on for 2–3 minutes. Rinse thoroughly with plenty of water. Allowing the conditioner to sit longer enhances its nourishing effects. The conditioner can also be massaged into the scalp for added hydration.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua*, Cetearyl Alcohol**, Glycerin, Distearoylethyl Dimonium Chloride**, Betaine**, Peat*, Caprylic\/Capric Triglyceride**, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice*, Benzyl Alcohol**, Panthenol**, Dehydroacetic Acid**, Simmondsia Chinensis (Jojoba) Seed Oil*, Juniperus Communis (Juniper berry) Fruit Oil*, Tocopherol**, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil**, Limonene***, Potassium Sorbate**, Sodium Benzoate\u003cstrong\u003e, Citric Acid\u003c\/strong\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e* Natural origin\u003cbr\u003e** Natural cosmetics approved ingredient\u003cbr\u003e*** Occurs naturally in essential oil\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"Nurme","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52880680517959,"sku":null,"price":14.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/nurme-balneological-peat-strenghtening-conditioner-250ml-2944215.webp?v=1765078819"}],"url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/collections\/palsamid.oembed","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}